        <Summary>Gtk+ frontend to su and sudo</Summary>
        <Description>GKSu is a library that provides a Gtk+ frontend to su and sudo. It supports login shells and preserving environment when acting as a su frontend. It is useful to menu items or other graphical programs that need to ask a user's password to run another program as another user.</Description>
        <License>GPLv2+</License>
